properties.title: MyGame
properties.addinjury:
if $health = 0 
		message = 'SORRY -- YOU DIE' game stop
	else
		health = ($health -1)
		message + 'OUCH!' 
	end
properties.movecar:
text tx 
	proximity POV 1
	tx = $proximity
	compare $tx 'forward'
	if( $compare = 0 )
	    call addinjury
	end
	square F forward
	tx = $square
	compare $tx 'none'
    if( $compare <> 0 )
		square R rightward
		compare $R.desc 'road'
		if( $compare = 0 )
	        move shiftright
        else
			square L leftward
			compare $L.desc 'road'
			if( $compare = 0 )
          		move shiftleft
          	end
        end
    else
		compare $F.desc 'road'
		if( $compare = 0 )
		  move forward
		  if( $move = 0 ) 
			square R rightward
		    compare $R.desc 'road'
		    if( $compare = 0 )
			  move rightward
			end
			if( $move = 0 )
			  square L leftward
		      compare $L.desc 'road'
		      if( $compare = 0 )
				move leftward
			  end
			end
		  end
		else
		  square R rightward
		  compare $R.desc 'road'
		  if( $compare = 0 )
		    move rightward
		    if( $move = 0 )
		      square L leftward
		      compare $L.desc 'road'
		      if( $compare = 0 )
			    move leftward
			  end
			end
		  else
		    square L leftward
		    compare $L.desc 'road'
		    if( $compare = 0 )
		      move leftward
			end
		  end
		end
	end
